description: Donovan Dent had 20 points in New Mexico's 83-77 win over San Jose State on Wednesday night.

headline: Clifford has 19 points, 17 rebounds and 6 assists to lead Colorado State over Loyola Marymount 83-54
description: Nique Clifford scored 19 points, grabbed 17 rebounds and had six assists as Colorado State beat Loyola Marymount 83-54 on Wednesday night.

headline: Akins scores 22, Denver downs Sacramento State 80-59
description: Sebastian Akins scored 22 points as Denver beat Sacramento State 80-59 on Wednesday night.

headline: Moore scores 16, Montana beats South Dakota State 71-67
description: Malik Moore had 16 points in Montana's 71-67 victory against South Dakota State on Wednesday night.

headline: North Dakota State earns 77-73 win against Weber State
description: Jacksen Moni had 22 points in North Dakota State's 77-73 win against Weber State on Wednesday night.

headline: Cook has 20 as Eastern Washington defeats North Dakota 87-81
description: Andrew Cook's 20 points helped Eastern Washington defeat North Dakota 87-81 on Wednesday night.

headline: Johnson's big 3-pointer late helps carry Texas past North Carolina State
description: Freshman Tre Johnson scored 18 points shooting 4 for 6 from 3-point range and Texas beat North Carolina State 63-59 in an SEC/ACC Challenge contest on Wednesday night.

headline: Collins and Edwards lead Vanderbilt over Virginia Tech 80-64 in SEC/ACC Challenge
description: Jason Edwards scored 19 points, MJ Collins added 15 and Vanderbilt cruised to an 80-64 victory over Virginia Tech on Wednesday night in the SEC/ACC Challenge.

headline: Chance McMillian, Darrion Williams lead Texas Tech to 76-62 victory over DePaul
description: Chance McMillian scored 22 points, Darrion Williams added 20 and Texas Tech defeated DePaul 76-62 on Wednesday night in the Big 12-Big East Battle.

headline: Christofilis scores 22 as Seattle downs Portland State 91-74
description: John Christofilis scored 22 points as Seattle beat Portland State 91-74 on Wednesday.
